{"tid":1159511,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"杜曹：所有人都知道，在法甲奪冠從來不是件容易的事","createTime":"2019-05-17T17:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T00:47:02.000Z","uid":38189,"like":12,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8eaf46ea9b76caf857c93027a79686a26cbae7d7","tid":1159511,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T17:47:59.000Z","msg":"巴黎主帥杜曹在新聞發布會上表示，球隊現在開始享受聯賽奪冠的喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;我們喜歡在我們的球迷面前踢球，那有一種獨特的氛圍。所有人都知道，在法甲奪冠從來不是一件容易的事，現在是時候享受和慶祝冠軍了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;我每天都在學習，所以我離開德甲，來到法國，我不斷地學習，這是我的目標。在這裡執教是一個巨大的挑戰，但也是一件很好的事情。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;對麥巴比來說，獲得金靴獎是極其重要的事情，他一直在為此努力。對我們來說，我們會盡量幫助他完成這個目標。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜曹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad12204d1d506c319e367d609d5a4fcc9b3a999","tid":1159511,"uid":60831,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T17:50:49.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑呀屌你老未"},{"pid":"16e1c3d61fb54fdf7efc65eaad0f66d0f31824a7","tid":1159511,"uid":46587,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"C朗：所有人都知道，在意甲奪冠從來不是件容易的事"},{"pid":"471bedf58a1e59cd156686bb34ef1b5ba99dc387","tid":1159511,"uid":119729,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T17:52:08.000Z","msg":"佢同緊其他法甲領隊講姐"},{"pid":"7ef9ab9042e1fcf9cdf5c192b07b0506ff1161e8","tid":1159511,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"仆街 睇完真心笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32631d41cf75d767a71444f7750a8ee62dce679e","tid":1159511,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T18:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢<span style=\"color: red;\">代</span>其他法甲領隊講姐</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cd80bd3ed8835c453f1331e22f870ce495736f87","tid":1159511,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32631d41cf7